{
  "stem": "1828.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By madrichim, by our leaders who had contacts with the outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could smell it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mother would say to us, children, the ovens are all active.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- you could smell it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Chimneys were smoking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you could hear them coming in, the transports at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those that were tattooed were the privileged ones, because that meant that you weren't going straight into-- to your death.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You-- you had a little time, and just wait for it to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that didn't mean that you didn't-- that you weren't sent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- just meant that not immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Either the ovens were overworked, or they were going to pause for another reason for a day or so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it went constantly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the meantime, our camp was organized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The men on one side, the women on the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And every day, we could see the men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We saw our father for about an hour every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was a very disciplined man, lean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he-- he knew how to fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was very-- I knew that if-- unless they killed him, he wouldn't just die of starvation or-- or because his morale was crushed, which the men-- men fell to very easily.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "For some reason-- it's a study I should make one day-- the women handled it emotionally better than the men.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- but the job they had given my father in the beginning was to carry stones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was the most idiotic work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a pile of stones which they carried from one place up the hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And two days later, they'd carry it from up there down back there again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is how they occupied the men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Maybe because men would have done something.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
